item.title: Projects
item.description: Check out some of the best projects I’ve worked on over the years. Golang Interview A github repo of interview questions I’ve completed in Golang separated by topic for concentrated study. Included in the readmes are mistakes, simple complexity analysis and extra things I personally learned from each question. Block the Youtube Feed A simple chrome extension that blocks the recommended videos and main feed on youtube to minimize distractions and maximize youtube productivity.

item.title: About
item.description: Incremental Reader. Software Engineer at X company. Creator of a few libraries, tools, and scripts. Building everyday. I didn’t start this journey always knowing what I loved to do, I have just slowly started to find it. A long time ago, I remember I talked to a friendly neighbor and asked him how he knew what he wanted to do when he grew up. He laughed and told me he still didn’t know.
